  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libgtop</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libgtop</application> package contains the
      <application>GNOME</application> top libraries.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
